ns4:Method.description: Search for experiments matching given criteria
ns4:Method.name: searchForExperiments

ns4:Method.description: return list of all persons who are principal investigators for some experiment
ns4:Method.name: getAllPrincipalInvestigators

ns4:Method.description: Begin an enumeration of experiments matching given criteria
ns4:Method.name: enumerateExperiments

ns4:Method.description: Returns a grid transfer reference which will retrieve the zip of all the files included in the download
ns4:Method.name: getFileContentsZipTransfer

ns4:Method.description: Returns an array of file content transfers for all files in the given request
ns4:Method.name: getFileContentsTransfers

ns4:Method.description: Returns a grid transfer reference for retrieving the given reference
ns4:Method.name: getFileContentsTransfer

ns4:Input.description: a DataSetRequest identifying the parsed data to be retrieved. The request must specify at least one hybridization or one file, and at least one quantitation type
ns4:Input.name: dataSetRequest

ns4:Exception.description: if the data sets for the hybridizations and/or files in the request are not consistent, e.g. do not correspond to the same design element list.
ns4:Exception.name: InconsistentDataSetsFault

ns4:Exception.description: if any of the hybridization, file or quantitation references in the dataSetRequest are not valid
ns4:Exception.name: NoEntityMatchingReferenceFault

ns4:Exception.description: if any of the hybridization, file or quantitation references in the dataSetRequest are not valid
ns4:Exception.name: IncorrectEntityTypeFault

ns4:Method.description: Searches for experiments using a keyword search across fields
ns4:Method.name: searchForExperimentsByKeyword

ns4:Method.description: Search for files matching given criteria
ns4:Method.name: searchForFiles

ns4:Method.description: Search for biomaterials matching given keyword
ns4:Method.name: searchForBiomaterialsByKeyword

ns4:Method.description: Returns an export of an experiment as a set of mage-tab IDF and SDRF, along with metadata for associated data files
ns4:Method.name: getMageTabExport

ns4:Method.description: returns a transfer reference for retrieving a zipped mage tab export of an experiment. The zip will include the idf and sdrf and all referenced data files
ns4:Method.name: getMageTabZipTransfer

ns4:Method.description: Search for quantitation types matching criteria
ns4:Method.name: searchForQuantitationTypes

ns4:Method.description: Search using an entity as example
ns4:Method.name: searchByExample
